snippet.textDisplay:
As a 46 yr Young man I'm on my Lunch Break watching this and about to tear up😢
I'm Born & Raised in the (336) and still here! My Mom is still living in the same house that my Grandfather built when she was a Lil Girl and its falling down and in God Awful shape!
Why am I telling y'all this is because I'm her Only Son and she has been in Remission from Breast Cancer for 12 yrs now. I told her back then that she had to stick around because I was going to get her a house one day some kind of a way!
God, Truly Does work in Mysterious Ways and I need y'all support.
No B.S.
For those of you who play Call of Duty
I am the Motivating Voice of Influence that reunited the Original Infinity Ward Developer's for the Current Modern Warfare Series.
The Reintroduction of their Main Character Captain Price is also do to me. When he Snipes the Bad Guy in the first Campaign Mission while it takes the Shot from On Top Of The Building is my Idea.
The Idea to do a Reboot of the Series also comes from my Tangible Expressions of Ideas as to how we could do away with the last 6-7 yrs of COD which have Sucked IMO...
By using the Matrix Movie as a example as to how we could act like they Never Existed!!
Its all in my Video
Titled: Call of Duty Black Ops4 Rant
By: Mr.CleanSS
Published May 18 2018
As a Older Gamer I missed the Good Ole Days of COD and that is what inspired me to record the video.
Doing So, I led Infinity Ward / Activision to the Lake and my Interllectual Formula led them to the Bank! While my Mom is Living in Poverty!
I'm currently waiting on my Copyright.
Please Like & Share
Thank you.
I do apologize for some of the Harsh Language it was all in the name of Passion for my Favorite Video Game Title..
